<item>
            <title>[LU-19617] the race to set/clear &quot;lqe_glbl_data&quot; between qmt_lvbo_init and qmt_work_lvbo_free </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19617</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;qmt_lvob_init holds the &quot;lqe_glbl_data_lock &quot;&lt;br/&gt;
qmt_lvbo_init finds the &quot;lqe-&amp;gt;lqe_glbl_data&quot; is not NULL, then it skips the setting&lt;br/&gt;
qmt_work_lvbo_free acquires the &quot;lqe_glbl_data_lock&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
qmt_work_lvbo_free set &quot;lqe-&amp;gt;lqe_glbl_data&quot; to NULL and frees the lqe_glbl_data&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the &quot;lqe-&amp;gt;lqe_glbl_data&quot; is NULL and could affect the following quota operations.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
